{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b26da783c9","title":"关于警察问题致华中局电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e8936d25c","index":0,"year":1945,"month":8,"day":15,"articleId":"b26da783c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b7c521cc4","name":"人民战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji20","name":"毛泽东全集第20卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji20.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji20":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f1cd808fe0","type":"paragraph","text":"关于警察问题致华中局电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b26da783c9"},{"id":"62ed85930a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年8月15日）关于各城市的警察，我方入城前，即应以军事机关命令他们负责维持秩序。入城后不可将警察拘捕起来，以免秩序无人维持，更易引起混乱，所有警察局长，在能服从我们军事管制命令的条件下，亦可暂时不加调换","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b26da783c9"},{"id":"5ebba109eb","type":"paragraph","text":"东心1945年8月，八路军和苏联红军在山海关会师。北平人民欢庆抗日战争的胜利。延安人民在欢庆抗日战争的胜利。《人民战争胜利万岁》（油画）","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b26da783c9"}],"page":{"id":"9310cd768f","publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b26da783c9","start":264,"end":267}}}},"__N_SSG":true}